# FilmCircle — Build Walkthrough

> **Status: Complete** ✅ | All phases 0–7 executed.

---

## What Was Built

A full-stack, zero-cost, community-based film review platform based on [Synoopsis_003.docx](file:///d:/College/Final%20project/Synoopsis_003.docx).

### Key Feature: 4-Option Review System
Instead of star ratings, every review is one of:
| Button | Meaning |
|---|---|
| ⏭️ Skip | Not worth watching |
| 🤔 Considerable | Watch if you have time |
| ✅ Go For It | Recommended |
| ⭐ Excellent | Must watch |

